dc_title_s: Allamakee County, Iowa, 1971, aerial photomosaic index
dc_description_s: Title supplied by cataloger based on information from sheet labels. Images are photoreductions of mosaics created from original aerial photographs. Designating symbol SP. Form of individual image numbering: SP-1MM-[number], SP-2MM-[number], SP-3MM-[number], or SP-4MM-[number]. Year Flown 1971. Flown by Park Aerial Surveys, Inc. Louisville, K.Y.
